    Page: 637
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Ecstasy=Mindlessness
By: Richard of Saint-Victor
---
For when the mind of man is carried beyond itself all the limits of human
reasoning are overpassed. For the whole system of human reasoning succumbs to
that which the soul perceives of the divine light, when she is raised above
herself and ravished in ecstasy. For what is the death of Rachel but the
failure of reason?
